dataset_id: BOREAS TF-04 CO2 and CH4 Chamber Flux Data from the SSA
title: BOREAS TF-04 CO2 and CH4 Chamber Flux Data from the SSA
summary: Contains fluxes of carbon dioxide and methane across the soil-air interface in four ages of jack pine forest at the Southern Study Area.  Gross and net flux of CO2 and flux of CH4 between soil and air are presented for 24 chamber sites in mature jack pine stands.
